These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, mirinda, water
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, ritmeester, old-henry, cain
1. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the left of the old-henry-smoker##5
2. the person drinking lemonade is not the alhambra-smoker##6
3. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
6. the alhambra-smoker is not the person drinking mirinda##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | lemonade   | water    | juice    | mirinda |
| Sport      | cain | alhambra | old-henry | ritmeester |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  nurse, project-manager, designer, bartender
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, grapefruit, lettuce, onion
1. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
2. the project-manager is somewhere to the left of the designer##5
3. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the bartender##5
4. the project-manager is not the person eating grapefruit##6
5. the person eating onion is on the left of the designer##1
6. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
7. the bartender is on the right of the nurse##1
8. the designer is somewhere to the left of the nurse##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | project-manager  | designer    | nurse | bartender    |
| Food       | onion | grapefruit | lettuce  | artichoke |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, lacrosse, sailing-polo, sailing
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, doctor, electrician, police-officer
1. the person who's sport is sailing is not the coach##6
2. the doctor is not the person who's sport is sailing-polo##6
3. the electrician is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
4. the doctor is the person who's sport is soccer##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the doctor##1
6. the person who's sport is soccer is in an odd position##4
7. the coach is on the far left or far right##3
8. the electrician is somewhere to the left of the police-officer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | sailing       | lacrosse  | soccer  | sailing-polo |
| Job        | electrician | police-officer | doctor | coach  |

