.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, iced-tea, milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, thriller, adventure, musical
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5
3. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5
4. the person drinking fanta is not the person watching musical movies##6
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is not the person drinking 7up##6
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
7. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | 7up        | milk | iced-tea | fanta |
| Transport   | musical | martial-arts | thriller     | adventure   |

