.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, baking, chess, fishing
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, colombian, indian, polish
1. the australian is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is not the colombian##6
3. the australian is on the far right##1
4. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
5. the person who's hobby is chess is the person who's hobby is chess##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the left of the australian##5
7. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##5
8. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
9. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the left of the polish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | baking | chess    | writing  | fishing   |
| Nationality   | indian  | polish | colombian | australian |

