.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk, soy-milk, tea
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, bluemaster, dunhill, chaman
1. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
2. the chaman-smoker is somewhere to the left of the dunhill-smoker##5
3. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
4. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
6. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
7. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
8. the person drinking milk is not the chaman-smoker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | milk  | 7up        | soy-milk      | tea          |
| Job        | bolivar | bluemaster | chaman | dunhill |

