.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, hedgehog, rabbit
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, bellflower, zinnia, iris
1. the person who growsamaryllis is not the owner of the ferret##6
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person who growsiris is the person who growsiris##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is not the person who growsiris##6
6. the person who growsbellflower is not the owner of the fish##6
7. the person who growsiris is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | hedgehog | ferret        | rabbit  | fish     |
| Sport   | amaryllis     | iris | bellflower | zinnia |

