.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, blue, amber, aquamarine
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, indie, pop
1. the person who likes coral is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
2. the fan electronic is somewhere to the left of the person who likes coral##5
3. the fan indie is not the person who likes amber##6
4. the person who likes blue is between the fan pop and the person who likes amber##2
5. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
6. the fan electronic is between the fan disco and the person who likes coral##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | amber | blue    | coral | aquamarine |
| Music-Genre   | disco         | electronic | pop   | indie     |

