.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, blueberry, cucumber, grapes
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, romance, fantasy, sports
1. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##5
2. the person eating grapes is not the person watching horror movies##6
3. the person watching romance movies is the person eating grapes##1
4. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
5. the person watching fantasy movies is not the person eating grapes##6
6. the person eating blueberry is not the person watching horror movies##6
7. the person eating cucumber is somewhere to the left of the person eating blueberry##5
8. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | asparagus  | cucumber | blueberry | grapes |
| Transport   | fantasy | horror     | sports     | romance    |

