.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-13::.
House: victorian, cape-cod, modern, wooden
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, romance, time-travel, western
1. the victorian house is somewhere to the right of the cape-cod house##5
2. the cape-cod house is not the person watching romance movies##6
3. the victorian house is the person watching western movies##1
4. the modern house is somewhere to the right of the person watching romance movies##5
5. the victorian house is between the cape-cod house and the person watching adventure movies##2
6. the cape-cod house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | wooden | cape-cod      | victorian | modern   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance     | time-travel | western   | adventure |

