3. the fan hip-hop is on the right of the fan metal##1
4. the fan hip-hop is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
5. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the fan funk##5
6. the fan funk is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | almond-milk | iced-tea | water      | mirinda   |
| Transport   | indie  | funk   | metal | hip-hop |

 